# Portfolio Management Platform

### 15-Minute Pitch + Demo Deck (Condensed)

---

## Slide 1 – Title & One-Liner (30 sec)

**Portfolio Management Platform**
*Replacing Excel-based portfolio chaos with a centralized, intelligent system*

Audience: Portfolio Managers | Reviewers | Stakeholders

---

## Slide 2 – Problem Statement (2 min)

### What’s Broken Today

Portfolio managers today:

* Maintain **multiple Excel files per client**
* Track **stocks, crypto, bonds, FDs, commodities separately**
* Manually calculate:

  * Portfolio value
  * Profit / loss
  * Asset allocation

Challenges:

* No centralized portfolio view
* Manual price updates
* Manual email reporting
* No real-time or historical insights

**Result:** Time-consuming, error-prone, and impossible to scale

---

## Slide 3 – Core Pain Points (1 min)

### Why Excel Fails at Scale

* Heavy manual effort
* High risk of calculation errors
* No live market data
* Poor portfolio visibility
* No automation
* Breaks down as client count grows

---

## Slide 4 – Solution Overview (1.5 min)

### Our Product

A **centralized, secure, automated Portfolio Management Platform** that replaces scattered Excel workflows.

**What it does:**

* One system for all clients & assets
* Live portfolio valuation
* Automated analytics & reporting

---

## Slide 5 – Key Capabilities (1 min)

### What the Platform Delivers

* Email-based OTP authentication
* Centralized user & portfolio management
* Excel / CSV bulk asset upload
* Live asset price fetching
* Portfolio analytics & charts
* Automated email statements
* Investment news integration
* 6-month historical tracking

---

## Slide 6 – User Flow & Security (1 min)

### Secure Access Model

Flow:
Signup → Email OTP → Verify → Login → Dashboard

Security highlights:

* No login without registration
* Time-bound OTP via SMTP
* Only verified users access portfolios

---

## Slide 7 – Excel Ingestion (Demo Slide) (1.5 min)

### How We Kill Excel Chaos

* Users upload Excel / CSV files
* Backend parses & validates data
* Assets mapped into structured models:

  * Stocks
  * Crypto
  * Bonds
  * Commodities

**Value:**

* Bulk upload instead of manual entry
* Clean, searchable, centralized data

---

## Slide 8 – Dashboard & Analytics (Demo Slide) (2 min)

### What Managers See

Dashboard shows:

* Live total portfolio value
* Asset-wise allocation
* Profit / loss summary

Analytics:

* Asset distribution charts
* Portfolio performance trends
* High-level risk visibility

---

## Slide 9 – Live Pricing & News (1.5 min)

### Real-Time Intelligence

**Live Pricing:**

* Python-based pricing microservice
* Fetches real-time prices via market APIs
* Keeps portfolio valuation always current

**News Integration:**

* Real-time investment & market news
* Helps managers make informed decisions

---

## Slide 10 – Automated Reporting (1 min)

### Zero Manual Effort

* System auto-generates portfolio statements
* Includes:

  * Portfolio value
  * Asset breakdown
  * Profit / loss
* Statements emailed automatically to users

**No Excel. No manual emails.**

---

## Slide 11 – System Architecture (1.5 min)

### Built to Scale

**Frontend:** HTML, CSS, JavaScript
**Backend:** Spring Boot (REST APIs, business logic, security)
**Database:** Relational DB (users, portfolios, assets)
**Microservice:** Python pricing service
**Integrations:** SMTP, Market APIs, News APIs

**Why it scales:** modular, API-driven, decoupled services

---

## Slide 12 – Business & Technical Value (1 min)

### Why This Matters

**For Portfolio Managers:**

* Single dashboard replaces Excel
* Faster decisions
* Better client communication
* Easy scalability

**Technically:**

* Secure authentication
* Clean architecture
* Microservice-based pricing

---

## Slide 13 – Future Scope: AI Chatbot (1 min)

### Where This Goes Next

* AI chatbot interface
* Predefined questions:

  * “How is my portfolio performing?”
  * “Which asset has the highest return?”
* Future LLM-driven insights & recommendations

---

## Slide 14 – Final Slide (30 sec)

### Why This Product Wins

* Replaces Excel chaos with intelligence
* Automates portfolio tracking & reporting
* Delivers real-time insights
* Secure, scalable, and future-ready

**A modern platform for modern portfolio management.**
